{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/iterate-odd-numbers-with-a-for-loop","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Iteriraj Neparne Brojeve Pomocu for Petlje","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>for petlje ne moraju iterirati jedan po jedan korak. Menjanjem <code>final-expression</code> dela mozemo brojati po parnim brojevima.</p>\n<p>Pocinjemo sa <code>i = 0</code> i petlja se izvrsava dok je <code>i &#x3C; 10</code>. Povecavacemo <code>i</code> za 2 u svakoj iteraciji koristeci <code>i += 2</code>.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">const ourArray = [];\n\nfor (let i = 0; i &#x3C; 10; i += 2) {\n  ourArray.push(i);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>ourArray</code> ce sada biti <code>[0, 2, 4, 6, 8]</code>. Hajde da promenimo <code>initialization</code> kako bismo brojali neparne brojeve.</p>\n</section>","id":"56104e9e514f539506016a5c","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ubacite neparne brojeve od 1 do 9 u <code>myArray</code> koristeci <code>for</code> petlju.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18212,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/iterate-odd-numbers-with-a-for-loop"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nconst myArray = [];\n\n// Only change code below this line\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Za ovo treba da koristite <code>for</code> petlju.</p>","testString":"assert(/for\\s*\\([^)]+?\\)/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{